messages.message: @jack.robbins @Serena saw this task (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-4408) is marked as a blocker. Do we know when we'll start implementing this

we still need to do capacity planning for Q3 - so Q3 _at the earliest. B_ut logically, if a customer needs runtime configs (many enterprise solutions do), and needs to use GT sets (I imagine most do), they're in trouble, which is why I increased the priority.
